@page "/privacypolicy"
@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_AuthLayout.cshtml";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<style>
.page-hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e1b6e,#3730a3);color:#fff;padding:48px 0 36px;margin:-24px -15px 0}
.page-hero h1{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.4rem);font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px}
.policy-wrap{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto}
.pc{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:14px;padding:28px;margin-bottom:14px}
.pc h2{font-size:1.08rem;font-weight:700;color:#1e1b6e;margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.pc p,.pc li{font-size:.88rem;color:#64748b;line-height:1.8}
.pc ul{padding-left:18px;margin-bottom:0}
.pc li{margin-bottom:5px}
.pc strong{color:#374151}
.snum{width:26px;height:26px;background:#3730a3;color:#fff;border-radius:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:.76rem;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0}
.hbox{border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;margin-top:10px;font-size:.82rem}
.hbox.green{background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #bbf7d0;color:#15803d}
.hbox.amber{background:#fef3c7;border:1px solid #fde68a;color:#92400e}
</style>

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="container policy-wrap">
    <span style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25);border-radius:20px;padding:4px 14px;font-size:.77rem;font-weight:500;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:14px"><i class="bi bi-shield-fill-check me-1"></i>DPDP Act 2023 Compliant</span>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="opacity:.85;font-size:.88rem">S3KN Software Solutions Pvt. Ltd. — GP MNREGA Platform</p>
    <small style="opacity:.6;font-size:.78rem">Last updated: 01 January 2025 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Effective immediately</small>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container py-4">
  <div class="policy-wrap">

    <div class="pc" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e1b6e,#3730a3);color:#fff;border:none">
      <div class="d-flex gap-3 align-items-start">
        <i class="bi bi-shield-fill-check" style="font-size:2rem;color:#4ade80;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px"></i>
        <div>
          <h5 style="font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px">India's Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023</h5>
          <p style="opacity:.9;font-size:.87rem;margin:0">This Privacy Policy complies with the <strong style="color:#fff">DPDP Act 2023</strong>. As a <strong style="color:#fff">Data Fiduciary</strong>, S3KN Software Solutions Pvt. Ltd. processes your personal data only for lawful purposes with your consent or other permissible grounds, protected with appropriate security safeguards.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pc">
      <h2><div class="snum">1</div>Who We Are (Data Fiduciary)</h2>
      <p><strong>S3KN Software Solutions Pvt. Ltd.</strong><br/>SY 953/*/P2 107, Sai Park Ring Road, Vijayapur – 586 109, Karnataka, India<br/>Email: <a href="mailto:admin@gpmnrega.com" style="color:#3730a3">admin@@gpmnrega.com</a></p>
      <div class="hbox green"><i class="bi bi-person-badge me-1"></i>For all DPDP Act requests and grievances, email <strong>admin@@gpmnrega.com</strong> with subject "Data Rights Request". We respond within 30 days.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="pc">
      <h2><div class="snum">2</div>Personal Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect only the minimum data necessary (principle of <strong>data minimisation</strong> under DPDP Act 2023):</p>
      <div class="table-responsive mt-2">
        <table class="table table-sm" style="font-size:.84rem">
          <thead style="background:#f8faff"><tr><th style="font-weight:600;color:#374151">Data</th><th style="font-weight:600;color:#374151">Purpose</th><th style="font-weight:600;color:#374151">Legal Basis</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody style="color:#64748b">
            <tr><td>Name, Email, Phone</td><td>Account creation &amp; communication</td><td>Consent / Contract</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Panchayat Code, GP Name, Block, District, Vidhan/Lok Sabha</td><td>Generating correct reports with regional data</td><td>Contract</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Payment transaction ID</td><td>Subscription management &amp; receipts</td><td>Contract / Legal obligation</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Login timestamps, IP (hashed)</td><td>Security &amp; fraud prevention</td><td>Legitimate use (S.7 DPDP)</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Session cookies</td><td>Keeping you logged in, CSRF protection</td><td>Consent / Contract</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <div class="hbox green"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-1"></i><strong>We do NOT collect:</strong> Aadhaar, biometric data, bank account details, health data, caste, religion, political beliefs, or any Sensitive Personal Data under Indian law.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="pc">
      <h2><div class="snum">3</div>How We Use Your Data</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Consent (S.6):</strong> By registering, you consent to processing your data to provide the GP MNREGA service.</li>
        <li><strong>Contractual obligation:</strong> To fulfil your subscription, generate reports, and send transactional emails.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal obligation:</strong> To maintain financial records under GST and Income Tax Act.</li>
        <li><strong>Legitimate use (S.7):</strong> Security logging and fraud prevention using anonymised data.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="hbox amber"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill me-1"></i><strong>We will never use your data for:</strong> Unsolicited marketing, profiling, selling to third parties, or any purpose not listed above.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="pc">
      <h2><div class="snum">4</div>When We Share Your Data</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Payment processor:</strong> Name, email, phone shared with our UPI gateway solely to process transactions.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Cloud Translate:</strong> Panchayat/block/constituency names (no personal identifiers) sent to generate Kannada translations.</li>
        <li><strong>Legal requirements:</strong> Disclosure to law enforcement only when required by a valid legal order under Indian law.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="hbox green"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-1"></i><strong>We never sell, rent, or trade your personal data</strong> to any marketing company, data broker, or third party for commercial purposes.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="pc">
      <h2><div class="snum">5</div>Your Rights Under the DPDP Act, 2023</h2>
      <div class="row g-3">
        <div class="col-md-6"><div class="d-flex gap-3 p-3 rounded-2" style="background:#f8faff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0"><i class="bi bi-eye-fill" style="color:#3730a3;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px"></i><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:.86rem;color:#374151">Right to Access (S.11)</div><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:#64748b">Request summary of your data and processing purposes.</div></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-md-6"><div class="d-flex gap-3 p-3 rounded-2" style="background:#f8faff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0"><i class="bi bi-pencil-square" style="color:#3730a3;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px"></i><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:.86rem;color:#374151">Right to Correction (S.12)</div><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:#64748b">Request correction via account settings or email.</div></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-md-6"><div class="d-flex gap-3 p-3 rounded-2" style="background:#f8faff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0"><i class="bi bi-trash3-fill" style="color:#3730a3;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px"></i><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:.86rem;color:#374151">Right to Erasure (S.12)</div><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:#64748b">Request deletion — processed within 30 days.</div></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-md-6"><div class="d-flex gap-3 p-3 rounded-2" style="background:#f8faff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0"><i class="bi bi-x-circle-fill" style="color:#3730a3;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px"></i><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:.86rem;color:#374151">Right to Withdraw Consent (S.13)</div><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:#64748b">Withdraw consent at any time by closing your account.</div></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-md-6"><div class="d-flex gap-3 p-3 rounded-2" style="background:#f8faff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill" style="color:#3730a3;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px"></i><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:.86rem;color:#374151">Right to Grievance Redressal (S.13)</div><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:#64748b">Complain to us or escalate to the Data Protection Board of India.</div></div></div></div>
        <div class="col-md-6"><div class="d-flex gap-3 p-3 rounded-2" style="background:#f8faff;border:1px solid #e2e8f0"><i class="bi bi-person-x-fill" style="color:#3730a3;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px"></i><div><div style="font-weight:600;font-size:.86rem;color:#374151">Right to Nominate (S.14)</div><div style="font-size:.78rem;color:#64748b">Nominate a person to exercise your rights in case of death or incapacity.</div></div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pc">
      <h2><div class="snum">6</div>Cookies</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Authentication cookie (.S3KN_AUTH2):</strong> HttpOnly, Secure — keeps you logged in. Cannot be read by JavaScript. Expires after 24 hours of inactivity.</li>
        <li><strong>Anti-forgery token:</strong> Prevents CSRF attacks on forms.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do <strong>not</strong> use advertising cookies, third-party tracking, or analytics. Disabling cookies will prevent login.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pc">
      <h2><div class="snum">7</div>Security</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>HTTPS / TLS 1.2+:</strong> All data in transit is encrypted.</li>
        <li><strong>BCrypt password hashing:</strong> We cannot read your password.</li>
        <li><strong>HttpOnly cookies:</strong> Auth cookies protected against XSS theft.</li>
        <li><strong>Data breach notification:</strong> Affected users and the Data Protection Board notified as required under DPDP Act 2023 (S.8).</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="pc">
      <h2><div class="snum">8</div>Data Retention</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account data:</strong> Deleted within 30 days of account deletion request.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment records:</strong> Retained 7 years under Income Tax Act and GST law.</li>
        <li><strong>Server logs:</strong> 90 days, no personal data.</li>
        <li><strong>Contact form submissions:</strong> 12 months then deleted.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="pc">
      <h2><div class="snum">9</div>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>GP MNREGA is intended for adult government officials. We do not knowingly collect data from persons under 18, in accordance with <strong>Section 9 of the DPDP Act 2023</strong>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pc">
      <h2><div class="snum">10</div>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>Material changes will be notified to registered users by email and the "Last updated" date revised. Continued use constitutes acceptance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pc" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f0fdf4,#d1fae5);border-color:#bbf7d0">
      <h2 style="color:#15803d"><div class="snum" style="background:#059669">?</div>Questions or Complaints</h2>
      <p style="color:#374151">Email <a href="mailto:admin@gpmnrega.com?subject=Data Rights Request" style="color:#059669;font-weight:600">admin@@gpmnrega.com</a> with subject "Data Rights Request". If unsatisfied with our response, you may escalate to the <strong>Data Protection Board of India</strong> under DPDP Act 2023.</p>
      <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-sm" style="background:#059669;color:#fff;border-radius:8px"><i class="bi bi-envelope me-1"></i> Contact Us</a>
        <a href="/termsandconditions" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary" style="border-radius:8px"><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-check me-1"></i> Terms &amp; Conditions</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
